OL,3,CCryptosporidium cases linked to farm
OL,4,Cshop increases with some put in
OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,FThe number of confirmed
OL,8,FCryptosporidium cases linked to a
OL,9,FCowbridge farm shop has now reached 74
OL,10,Fwith some needing hospital treatment,
OL,11,FPublic Health Wales (PHW) has said.
OL,13,FThe outbreak has resulted in 16 people
OL,14,Fhaving to stay in hospital for at
OL,15,Fleast one night after being linked
OL,16,Fwith visits to Cowbridge Farm Shop at
OL,17,FMarlborough Grange Farm, in the Vale
OL,18,Fof Glamorgan.
