OL,7,FCryptosporidium is a parasite which
OL,8,Fcan cause gastrointestinal illness and
OL,9,Fis often associated with contact with
OL,10,Fanimals, especially young farm animals
OL,11,Flike calves and lambs.
OL,13,FA PHW spokesperson said: "Due to the
OL,14,Fincubation period of the infection, it
OL,15,Fis expected that this number may
OL,16,Fcontinue to increase in the coming
OL,17,Fweek.
OL,19,F"The farm has voluntarily ceased all
OL,20,Fpublic animal feeding activities and
OL,21,Fis cooperating with the investigation."
