OL,7,FThe update on confirmed cases comes
OL,8,Fafter a multi-agency outbreak control
OL,9,Fteam held its third meeting on
OL,10,FThursday, 8 May.
OL,12,FSu Mably, consultant in health
OL,13,Fprotection for Public Health Wales,
OL,14,Fsaid: "Although cryptosporidium
OL,15,Finfection is usually mild and clears
OL,16,Fup on its own, it can cause more
OL,17,Fserious illness in young children and
OL,18,Fpeople with weakened immune systems.
