OL,7,FPHW advice on reducing the risk of
OL,8,Finfection if visiting farms includes:
OL,10,FThose who have been unwell with the
OL,11,Fsymptoms following a visit to a farm
OL,12,Fare advised to take extra care not to
OL,13,Fspread the infection, and avoid
OL,14,Fswimming for two weeks after symptoms
OL,15,Fhave ceased.
